{
  "page": "Brotherhood of Bones",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Brotherhood of Bones</b> was a brotherhood of <a href=\"/index.php/Pirates\" title=\"Pirates\">pirates</a> and corsairs that settled on the <a href=\"/index.php/Basilisk_Isles\" title=\"Basilisk Isles\">Basilisk Isles</a> more than a century after the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Death\" title=\"Red Death\">Red Death</a> killed most people in them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_basilisk_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_basilisk_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brotherhood_of_Bones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Brotherhood settled on the <a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Flies\" title=\"Isle of Flies\">Isle of Flies</a> soon after <a href=\"/index.php/Xandarro_Xhore\" title=\"Xandarro Xhore\">Xandarro Xhore</a> established on <a href=\"/index.php/Ax_Isle\" title=\"Ax Isle\">Ax Isle</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_basilisk_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_basilisk_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Brotherhood_of_Bones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-re